          <span class="challenge-icon">⚠</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Experience Letter Details</strong>
            <p>DHA requires specific information in experience letters: exact dates, job title, department, responsibilities, and authorized signatures. We format translations to highlight this information clearly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
