          <p>Send your documents via WhatsApp to <a href="https://wa.me/971508620217">+971 50 862 0217</a>. We'll assess what you have, identify any missing documents, and provide a quote within 15 minutes during working hours.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="start-option">
          <h4>Option 2: Email Submission</h4>
          <p>Email scanned documents to info@onlinetranslation.ae with "DHA DataFlow Translation" in subject line. Include your DataFlow case number if you've already applied.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="start-option">
          <h4>Option 3: Coordinate with Your Consultant</h4>
          <p>If you're using a healthcare licensing consultant, we can coordinate directly with them to align translation delivery with your DataFlow timeline.</p>
        </div>
